data.description: Experience tranquility, serenity & views  on this expansive 16.12-acre property that presents boundless opportunities. This property boasts a charming 1782 sq ft home and a versatile garage/shop (approx. 720 sq ft).  The 3-bed, 2-bath home is thoughtfully designed with a split floor plan, offering ample space. Enjoy various living spaces, including a formal living room, a cozy family room with wood stove, & a welcoming dining room.  The well-equipped kitchen features abundant cabinet space, an island, a breakfast nook area, & an eating bar. The spacious primary bedroom includes an en-suite bathroom complete with dual vanities, a soaking tub, & a walk-in shower.  Step outside onto the covered rear deck or the side uncovered deck, offering you the choice of shade or open skies. Embrace the possibilities that this property affords for a peaceful and idyllic lifestyle.  Buyers with an adequate VA Certificate of Eligibility may assume existing mortgage with 2.625% interest rate.
